{
  "page": "Loreon Lannister (son of Jason)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/50px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/75px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/100px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Loreon Lannister</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/50px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/75px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/100px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Lord of Casterly Rock\">Lord of Casterly Rock</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Shield_of_Lannisport\" title=\"Shield of Lannisport\">Shield of Lannisport</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_West\" title=\"Warden of the West\">Warden of the West</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_126_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">126&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/136_AC\" title=\"136 AC\">136</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/196_AC\" title=\"196 AC\">196&#160;AC</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister\" title=\"Jason Lannister\">Jason Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\nLady <a href=\"/index.php/Johanna_Lannister\" title=\"Johanna Lannister\">Johanna Westerling</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Loreon Lannister</b> was the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Shield_of_Lannisport\" title=\"Shield of Lannisport\">Shield of Lannisport</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_West\" title=\"Warden of the West\">Warden of the West</a>, and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Loreon_Lannister_(son_of_Jason)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Loreon was the son of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister\" title=\"Jason Lannister\">Jason Lannister</a> and his wife, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Johanna_Lannister\" title=\"Johanna Lannister\">Johanna Westerling</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaftermath_-_the_hour_of_the_wolf.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> He had five trueborn sisters, including <a href=\"/index.php/Cerelle_Lannister_(daughter_of_Jason)\" title=\"Cerelle Lannister (daughter of Jason)\">Cerelle</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyshara_Lannister\" title=\"Tyshara Lannister\">Tyshara</a>, as well as several <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> half-sisters.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/130_AC\" title=\"130 AC\">130&#160;AC</a>, when Loreon was four years old, his father Jason died during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_the_Red_Fork\" title=\"Battle at the Red Fork\">Battle at the Red Fork</a>. Loreon subsequently became the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Lord of Casterly Rock\">Lord of Casterly Rock</a>. His mother, the Dowager Lady Johanna, ruled as his <a href=\"/index.php/Regent\" title=\"Regent\">regent</a> during his <a href=\"/index.php/Customs#Age_of_majority\" title=\"Customs\">minority</a>. During the regency, his mother waged <a href=\"/index.php/Struggle_for_power\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Struggle for power\">war</a> on the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> in his name.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Greyjoy_(son_of_Dalton)\" title=\"Rodrik Greyjoy (son of Dalton)\">Rodrik Greyjoy</a>, one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Salt_son\" title=\"Salt son\">salt sons</a> of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a>, was made Loreon's <a href=\"/index.php/Fool\" title=\"Fool\">fool</a> after being captured and <a href=\"/index.php/Eunuch\" title=\"Eunuch\">gelded</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands_-_the_red_kraken.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands_-_the_red_kraken.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Loreon_Lannister_(son_of_Jason)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyph